            "description": "A Motion Postcard is a unique online audiovisual format focused on the documentation and promotion of 'human creative rituals' throughout the world.\nThe project is a professional partnership between two cousins who are passionate about exploring the world through the principles of creative fair trade.\nOur work documents events, performances, ceremonies, traditional stories and nature, trough a hands-on, community-based style, delivering high quality audiovisual products for the upcoming Internet.\nThese products are ideal means for documentation and promotion of cultural events, festivals, gatherings, performances, ceremonies or tour destinations.",
